{
  "abstract": "Methods for the detection and indentification of plant viruses are described in this manual with particular emphasis on detection of important virus diseases of ICRISAT mandate crops.  These include protein-based (ELISA and Western immunoblotting) and nucleic acid-based (PCR, RT-PCR and dot-blot hybridization) techniques.",
